dashboard.definition:
{
  "title": "GreenZone Platform Observability - Setup",
  "visualizations": {
    "viz_setup_instructions": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "# Welcome to GreenZone Platform Observability!\n\n## Quick Setup Required\n\nBefore using the dashboards, configure your data sources by editing the index macros.\n\n### Step 1: Edit Macros\n\nNavigate to: **Settings → Advanced Search → Search Macros**\n\nFilter by: `greenzone_index_`\n\n### Step 2: Configure Each Index\n\nUpdate these macros to match YOUR Splunk indexes:\n\n| Macro Name | Default Value | Your Value |\n|------------|---------------|------------|\n| `greenzone_index_infrastructure` | `index=os OR index=infrastructure OR index=metrics` | Update to your infra indexes |\n| `greenzone_index_logs` | `index=main OR index=application OR index=logs` | Update to your log indexes |\n| `greenzone_index_endpoints` | `index=endpoint OR index=os OR index=windows OR index=linux` | Update to your endpoint indexes |\n| `greenzone_index_network` | `index=network OR index=firewall OR index=proxy` | Update to your network indexes |\n\n### Step 3: Choose Data Source Type\n\nEdit the `infrastructure_metrics_source` macro:\n\n```\n[infrastructure_metrics_source]\ndefinition = `infrastructure_metrics_source_YOUR_TYPE`\n```\n\nReplace `YOUR_TYPE` with:\n- `splunk` - Splunk infrastructure (_introspection)\n- `linux` - Linux/Unix systems\n- `windows` - Windows systems\n- `vmware` - VMware vSphere\n- `aws` - AWS CloudWatch\n- `generic` - Custom metrics\n\n### Step 4: Verify Configuration\n\nRun this search to test:\n```spl\n| `infrastructure_health_metrics`\n| head 10\n```\n\nYou should see data with fields: `host, cpu_pct, mem_pct, disk_pct, health`\n\n### Step 5: Start Using Dashboards\n\nOnce configured, access:\n- **Infrastructure Health** - Resource monitoring\n- **Log Analytics** - Log volume and errors\n- **Endpoint Monitor** - Agent health\n- **Traffic Insights** - Network visibility\n\n---\n\n## Need Help?\n\nSee the **COMPLETE_SETUP_GUIDE.md** in the app directory for detailed configuration instructions.\n\n---\n\n**Quick Links:**\n- [Settings → Search Macros](/manager/search/admin/macros)\n- [Complete Setup Guide](#)\n- [Documentation](#)\n"
      }
    },
    "viz_index_test": {
      "type": "splunk.table",
      "title": "Test Your Index Configuration",
      "description": "This shows what indexes are available in your Splunk environment",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_available_indexes"
      },
      "options": {
        "count": 20
      }
    },
    "viz_data_test": {
      "type": "splunk.table",
      "title": "Sample Data Test - Infrastructure",
      "description": "If you see data here, your infrastructure configuration is working",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_infrastructure_test"
      },
      "options": {
        "count": 10
      }
    }
  },
  "dataSources": {
    "ds_available_indexes": {
      "type": "ds.search",
      "options": {
        "query": "| eventcount summarize=false index=* index=_* | dedup index | eval \"Suggested For\"=case(match(index, \"(?i)infra|os|metric|vmware|aws\"), \"Infrastructure\", match(index, \"(?i)log|app|main\"), \"Logs\", match(index, \"(?i)endpoint|windows|linux|mac\"), \"Endpoints\", match(index, \"(?i)network|firewall|proxy|fw\"), \"Network\", match(index, \"(?i)_internal\"), \"Splunk Internal (Logs)\", match(index, \"(?i)_introspection\"), \"Splunk Infrastructure\", 1=1, \"Other\") | table index, count, \"Suggested For\" | rename index as \"Index Name\", count as \"Event Count\" | sort -count",
        "queryParameters": {
          "earliest": "-24h",
          "latest": "now"
        }
      }
    },
    "ds_infrastructure_test": {
      "type": "ds.search",
      "options": {
        "query": "| `infrastructure_health_metrics` | head 10 | table _time, host, cpu_pct, mem_pct, disk_pct, health | rename _time as \"Time\", host as \"Host\", cpu_pct as \"CPU %\", mem_pct as \"Memory %\", disk_pct as \"Disk %\", health as \"Health\"",
        "queryParameters": {
          "earliest": "-24h",
          "latest": "now"
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "layout": {
    "type": "grid",
    "structure": [
      {
        "item": "viz_setup_instructions",
        "type": "block",
        "position": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 1200, "h": 800}
      },
      {
        "item": "viz_index_test",
        "type": "block",
        "position": {"x": 0, "y": 800, "w": 1200, "h": 400}
      },
      {
        "item": "viz_data_test",
        "type": "block",
        "position": {"x": 0, "y": 1200, "w": 1200, "h": 400}
      }
    ]
  }
}
